		{
			"type": "dialogue-action",
			"dialogue": "老板，来一杯冰啤和一份生鱼片寿司军舰卷。",
			"speaker": "Catherine",
			"headfigure": "Resources/Images/Characters/HeadFigure/Journalist.png",
			"sound": {
				"blip": "Resources/SE/blip.wav",
				"volume": 0.1,
				"frequency": 4
			}
		},

		{
			"type": "dialogue-action",
			"dialogue": "*老板给Catherine端上了一杯热气腾腾的白开水*",
			"speaker": "Narrator",
			"sound": {
				"blip": "Resources/SE/blip.wav",
				"volume": 0.1,
				"frequency": 4
			}
		},
		{
			"type": "dialogue-action",
			"dialogue": "请先喝杯水暖暖身子吧，Catherine。我待会儿给你做寿司。",
			"speaker": "Iktsuarpok",
			"headfigure": "Resources/Images/Characters/HeadFigure/Master.png",
			"sound": {
				"blip": "Resources/SE/blip.wav",
				"volume": 0.1,
				"frequency": 4
			}
		},
		{
			"type": "dialogue-action",
			"dialogue": "没有冰啤吗？冰啤总不会现做吧？",
			"speaker": "Catherine",
			"headfigure": "Resources/Images/Characters/HeadFigure/Journalist.png",
			"sound": {
				"blip": "Resources/SE/blip.wav",
				"volume": 0.1,
				"frequency": 4
			}
		},
		{
			"type": "dialogue-action",
			"dialogue": "没办法，最近几天客人比较多，冰啤也卖完了。",
			"speaker": "Iktsuarpok",
			"headfigure": "Resources/Images/Characters/HeadFigure/Master.png",
			"sound": {
				"blip": "Resources/SE/blip.wav",
				"volume": 0.1,
				"frequency": 4
			}
		},
		{
			"type": "stage-action",
			"params":["show-dialogue"]
		},
		{
			"type": "dialogue-action",
			"dialogue": "唉，好吧，待会儿见。",
			"headfigure": "Resources/Images/Characters/HeadFigure/Journalist.png",
			"speaker": "Catherine",
			"sound": {
				"blip": "Resources/SE/blip.wav",
				"volume": 0.1,
				"frequency": 4
			}
		},
		{
			"type": "dialogue-action",
			"dialogue": "先去准备一下食材吧。",
			"speaker": "Iktsuarpok",
			"headfigure": "Resources/Images/Characters/HeadFigure/Master.png",
			"sound": {
				"blip": "Resources/SE/blip.wav",
				"volume": 0.1,
				"frequency": 4
			}
		},
		{
			"type": "stage-action",
			"fade": 0.1,
			"wait": 0.5
		},
		{
			"type": "stage-action",
			"fade": -0.1,
			"wait": 0.5,
			"background": {
				"name": "Resources/Images/FishingBackground.png"
			}
		},
		{
			"type": "dialogue-action",
			"dialogue": "接下来是钓鱼和寿司模式的教学。",
			"speaker": "Narrator",
			"sound": {
				"blip": "Resources/SE/blip.wav",
				"volume": 0.1,
				"frequency": 4
			}
		},
		{
			"type": "dialogue-action",
			"dialogue": "本作中，你将扮演寿司店的老板Iktsuarpok。这家寿司店的特殊之处就在于所有的食材都\n是老板亲手采集的。",
			"speaker": "Narrator",
			"sound": {
				"blip": "Resources/SE/blip.wav",
				"volume": 0.1,
				"frequency": 4
			}
		},
		{
			"type": "dialogue-action",
			"dialogue": "从现在开始，我会向你传授钓鱼和做寿司的基本技巧。先从钓鱼模式开始吧。",
			"speaker": "Narrator",
			"sound": {
				"blip": "Resources/SE/blip.wav",
				"volume": 0.1,
				"frequency": 4
			}
		},
		{
			"type": "dialogue-action",
			"dialogue": "因为是教程关，所以即便失败了也没有关系。",
			"speaker": "Narrator",
			"sound": {
				"blip": "Resources/SE/blip.wav",
				"volume": 0.1,
				"frequency": 4
			}
		},
		
		{
			"type": "dialogue-action",
			"dialogue": "倒不如说，我们根本没有准备失败后的分支剧情（实诚）",
			"speaker": "Developer",
			"headfigure": "Resources/Images/Characters/HeadFigure/Developer.png",
			"sound": {
				"blip": "Resources/SE/blip.wav",
				"volume": 0.1,
				"frequency": 4
			}
		},
		{
			"type": "dialogue-action",
			"dialogue": "喂。      \n不要管他。我们继续教程。",
			"speaker": "Narrator",
			"sound": {
				"blip": "Resources/SE/blip.wav",
				"volume": 0.1,
				"frequency": 4
